Tubbles README
--------------
Set up local repo:
git remote add upstream http://git.suckless.org/st
git fetch upstream

Build and run:
rm -f config.h && make clean all && tic -sx st.info && ./st && make clean && rm -f config.h

Install:
rm -f config.h && make clean all && sudo make install
